URL : https://api.vistara.io/api/v2/serviceProvider/customAttributes/{attributeId}/values/{valueId}

METHOD : POST

HEADERS:
	Authorization : Bearer {accessToken}
	Content-Type : application/json
	Accept : application/json

EX : https://api.vistara.io/api/v2/serviceProvider/customAttributes/71/values/411

NOTE : This api can be used for updating the description of a custom attribute value (value cannot be updated , only description).

INPUT JSON / PAYLOAD :
{
  "description" : "update for description"
}

RESPONSE : 
{
  "id" : 411,
  "vlaue" : "value of the custom attribute value",
  "description" : "update for description"
}

RESPONSE CODE : 200 OK